    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this BMW E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This example has undergone essential preventive maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS service. The chassis remains taut with its original MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry. While the car exhibits minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical systems are dialed in for peak performance. It is a robust, analog machine ready for spirited canyon carving or track day duty.",
      "price": 33500.0,
